sections.text:
76-210.Estates in future; recognized.

Estates may be created to commence at a future day.

SourceR.S.1866, c. 43, § 57, p. 292;R.S.1913, § 6194;C.S.1922, § 5593;C.S.1929, § 76-108;R.S.1943, § 76-210.
